$ Excel: Create comma separated values from a (selected) range

Vertical, single column selection
code {
debug.print → development/languages/VBA/functions/join[vba.join](application.transpose(selection.value), ",")
code }

Horizontal, single row selection:
code {
debug.print → development/languages/VBA/functions/join[vba.join](application.transpose(application.transpose(selection.value)), ",")
code }

sa:
  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/functions/text-related/textjoin[`textJoin()`]
